<num value="11">十一</num>月</measure>猶衣夾衣揮扇云<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>　　<measure quantity="4" unit="years">
<num value="4">四</num>年</measure>
<pc>，</pc>進封桓交趾郡王<pc>。</pc>
